{"id":"312091522_On_the_number_of_gapped_repeats_with_arbitrary_gap","abstract":"For any functions $f(x)$, $g(x)$ from $\\mathbb {N}$ to $\\mathbb {R}$ we call repeats $uvu$ such that $g(|u|)\\le |v|\\le f(|u|)$ as {\\it $f,g$-gapped repeats}. We study the possible number of $f,g$-gapped repeats in words of fixed length~$n$. For quite weak conditions on $f(x)$, $g(x)$ we obtain an upper bound on this number which is linear to~$n$.","authors":["Roman Kolpakov"],"meta":["January 2017Theoretical Computer Science","DOI:10.1016/j.tcs.2018.03.007"],"references":["334383528_Optimal_bounds_for_computing_a-gapped_repeats","284579161_Longest_Gapped_Repeats_and_Palindromes","282403230_Efficiently_Finding_All_Maximal_alpha-gapped_Repeats","262234901_Towards_a_Solution_to_the_Runs_Conjecture","256606518_Searching_of_Gapped_Repeats_and_Subrepetitions_in_a_Word","226887935_Squares_cubes_and_time-space_efficient_string_searching","221314014_Finding_Maximal_Pairs_With_Bounded_Gap","220113559_An_Optimal_Algorithm_for_Computing_the_Repetitions_in_a_Word","320515764_Searching_of_gapped_repeats_and_subrepetitions_in_a_word","314669567_Optimal_Bounds_for_Computing_alpha_a_-gapped_Repeats","300569498_Longest_alpha_a_-Gapped_Repeat_and_Palindrome","283524587_A_faster_algorithm_for_computing_maximal_a-gapped_repeats_in_a_string","281793182_Combinatorics_on_Words","262363308_Computing_the_Maximal-Exponent_Repeats_of_an_Overlap-Free_String_in_Linear_Time","228057969_Algorithms_on_Stings_Trees_and_Sequences","222617299_Time-space-optimal_string_matching","221579989_Extracting_Powers_and_Periods_in_a_String_from_Its_Runs_Structure","221150475_On_Maximal_Repetitions_in_Words","220688462_Data_Compression_Methods_and_Theory","50855623_On_primary_and_secondary_repetitions_in_words","45908253_On_the_Maximal_Sum_of_Exponents_of_Runs_in_a_String","29869167_Linear_time_algorithms_for_finding_and_representing_all_the_tandem_repeats_in_a_string","2400590_Finding_Repeats_With_Fixed_Gap"]}